description: Invests in a broad set of short-term debt obligations across sectors, maturities and issuers.Pursues the benefits associated with indexing such as diversification and transparency of exposures, but with the ability to add value by making investment decisions using information embedded in current yields.Efficient portfolio management and trading process that is designed to enhance returns while seeking to reduce unnecessary risks and transaction costs.Built to fit seamlessly into an investor's asset allocation.
name: Avantis Short-Term Fixed Income ETF
